OL,3,CGirl, 14, in court accused of
OL,4,Cattempted murder after school knife
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FA teenage girl has appeared in court
OL,8,Faccused of attempting to murder two
OL,9,Fstudents and a teacher after a knife
OL,10,Fattack at a school.
OL,12,FThe girl, 14, who cannot be named
OL,13,Fbecause of her age, appeared via video-
OL,14,Flink at the Old Bailey.
OL,16,FShe was charged with three counts of
OL,17,Fattempted murder and two counts of
OL,18,Fpossessing a bladed article on school
OL,19,Fpremises on 9 June.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
