OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1781977680
OL,3,CGirl, 14, in court accused of
OL,4,Cattempted murder after school knife
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FGreater Manchester Police has
OL,8,Fpreviously said two pupils, both 14,
OL,9,Fand a male member of staff, 27, were
OL,10,Finjured in the incident in a form
OL,11,Fclass the Co-op Academy on Plant Hill
OL,12,FRoad, Blackley.
OL,14,FAll three victims have been discharged
OL,15,Ffrom hospital and suffered no serious
OL,16,Finjuries, GMP also said.
OL,18,FMrs Justice Cheema-Grubb told the
OL,19,Fdefendant the short preliminary
OL,20,Fhearing was to timetable the case.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
