FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1781977680
OL,3,CGirl, 14, in court accused of
OL,4,Cattempted murder after school knife
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FThe alleged attack is being
OL,8,Finvestigated by Counter Terrorism
OL,9,FPolice but has not been declared a
OL,10,Fterrorist incident.
OL,12,FThe girl was remanded into custody and
OL,13,Ftold to attend a plea and trial
OL,14,Fpreparation hearing at the same court
OL,15,Fon 23 October.
OL,17,FMrs Justice Cheema-Grubb told her: "In
OL,18,Fthe meantime, I am sure you will
OL,19,Funderstand it is in your best interest
OL,20,Fto co-operate with lawyers."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
